For dN/dS and R/C analyses run the codes in the following order

1 - Williams et al. 2023 flybase to NCBI
2- identifying orthologs
3- organize orthologs by folder
4- dN/dS and R/C calculations
5- Fig1 and ICC analyses; Fig4; Fig5 (any of these folder can be run after 4)


For SFS calculations:

1- SFS calculations
2- alpha and omega calculations


for annotation files and the files used for Fbgn to ncbi id conversion see "auxiliary files"